or one second the choice I made, does that make me unloyal? Now I am in a raiding guild. I am raiding places that on the Rathe I would probably still not be able to go, at least not with my guild. <br><br>My point is this: It's not a matter of loyalties, it is a matter of having fun. Even if it means saying goodbye. <br> <p><center><font size="-1"><p><i><b><a href="http://verbalsabre.50megs.com">Sabre</b></i></a></font><br>54 Channeler<br><a href="http://www.phoenixhorizon.com">Phoenix Horizon</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/umogglenottewbrite.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Moggle Nottewbrite</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=" http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif " BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master of Darkness </span><br>  Posts: 407<br> <font color=#333333>(10/7/01 9:55:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=192.topic&index=16>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Serious discussion (can that happen here?)</span><hr size=1> Eriic, are you the same Eriic in the game that I've been trying to track down? if so..Dude yer harder to catch than a greased ethiopian chicken. <br> if not, sorry to bother ya. <p><b>Gilgurth: and you'll die in what?  2 hits?<br>Onker: 3 if I'm lucky<br>Onker: I plan on being really lucky</b><br><br><font color=Red><b>Onker Purdydense<br> Level 45 Mojo Troll<br><center><fontcolor=orange><b> Master Of <br><center><a href="http://home.dencity.com/DescendingDarkness/"> <img src="http://home.dencity.com/DescendingDarkness/images/postlogo1.gif" width="316" heigh